<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9369</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊的鳍不断开合着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们闪耀着不同颜色的光芒，但休伊却一言不发。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了，休伊？”简问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我之前从未说过这样的话。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但你们确定这是你们想要的吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊看上去真的很担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不喜欢做孩子。”简说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人们总是告诉你要怎么怎么做，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50715</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但大人们就可以想做什么就做什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50716</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>休伊摇摇头，说：“不，简。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当大人比你想的要困难得多，但这是你的愿望。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的鳍暗了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62898</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，孩子们都感觉到手和腿一阵发痒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67928</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在长大！”鲍比大叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他胖胖的小肚子不见了，而且他在不断地长高。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快看我！”简叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88622</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的头发颜色变深了，个子也变高了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88623</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91540</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟的眼镜不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91541</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的脸变得更长了一些。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊不仅长高了，而且变得更壮了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103441</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的肚子凸了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103442</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“赛伊胖了！”鲍比开玩笑说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111305</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“闭嘴，鲍比。”赛伊嚷道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，孩子们感觉身上不痒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114743</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117029</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们停止了生长。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，孩子们已经不再是孩子了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们都是大人了。”休伊悲伤地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看看彼此。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊和鲍比都穿上了西装。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这条领带要勒死我了。”鲍比抱怨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟和简都穿上了裙子和高跟鞋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们都背着小包包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145977</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我现在是个女人了。”简开心地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152056</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154467</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了，我的任务完成了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，现在请你们......”休伊指向了那口井。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>长大了的赛伊用比以前更快的速度将木桶送回了井底。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！真快啊！”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171192</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是因为你更壮了。”简说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们都变了。”潘瑟感叹说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但这和他们第一个愿望的时候不太一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他们都变得美丽的时候，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191140</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看着彼此就像陌生人一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191141</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我能认出你。”潘瑟继续说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但你看上去......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201648</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了潘瑟？”简问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201649</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看上去老了。”潘瑟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207104</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“已经是这样了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210460</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们去镇上吧。”赛伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210461</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>已经变成大人的巴斯家的孩子们穿过了树林。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222171</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这对他们其中任何一个来说，都不是一段舒服的旅程。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222172</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这条领带太紧了！”鲍比继续抱怨着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我穿着这双高跟鞋根本不能走路。”潘瑟嚷嚷着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这件西服外套让我觉得太热了。”赛伊说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239823</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的小包总是往下掉。”简说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>等他们终于走到镇上的时候，所有人都松了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他们穿过人群时，其他成年人都看着他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“早上好。”赛伊用成年人的嗓音招呼道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“早上好。”人们也回应道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！他们觉得我们和他们一样啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他悄悄地跟他的兄弟姐妹说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276879</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得自己特别重要。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276880</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比说着挺直了身子，让自己显得更高一点。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>286108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们想做什么？”潘瑟问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>286109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288641</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道。”简说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288642</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的眼睛闪闪发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们去喝咖啡吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们一直都想知道咖啡是什么味道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305026</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们的父母和玛莎阿姨每天早上都会喝咖啡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305027</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309943</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“咖啡是给大人喝的。”妈妈总是这么说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309944</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315504</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等你们再长大一点儿就可以喝了。”爸爸曾经说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315505</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们找到了一家小小的咖啡店。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319987</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>324971</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们走到了柜台那里，点了四个大杯的咖啡。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>324972</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿，赛伊，我能不能吃芝士蛋糕？”鲍比问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>337844</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你知道关于甜点妈妈是怎么说的。”赛伊回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>337845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>342389</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>站在柜台后的男人奇怪地看着他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>342390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>345852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有其他要点的吗？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>345853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>348917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，没了，就点这些。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>348918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>352255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊用他低沉的新声音说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>352256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>357647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们端着咖啡去了靠近窗户的一张桌子那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>80</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>357648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>362788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们刚一坐下，简就脱掉了高跟鞋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>81</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>362789</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>368713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么每个人都可以穿着这样的鞋走路啊？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>82</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>368714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>372180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她揉着自己的脚抱怨着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>83</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>372181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>379012</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呸！”潘瑟把她喝到嘴里的咖啡又吐了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>84</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>379013</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>381310</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这太难喝了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>85</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>381311</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>386077</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妈妈和爸爸怎么会喜欢这种东西？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>86</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>386078</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>389113</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他孩子也尝了尝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>87</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>389114</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>393437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个味道很怪。”赛伊表示同意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>88</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>393438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>400855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在想为什么大人会喝这种苦苦的黑饮料。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>